  <brief_title>A Single-Centre Clinical Trial to Assess Steroid Induced Skin Atrophy on Healthy Skin</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single-Centre, Explorative, Randomised, Investigator-Blinded, Negative-Controlled, Phase I Clinical Trial With Intra-Individual Comparison of Treatments to Assess Steroid Induced Skin Atrophy on Healthy Skin</official_title>
